column5: MAX.... WHERE IN INDIANA ARE YOU FROM? I AM FROM NEW CASTLE, BUT I AM ORIGINALLY FROM GREENWOOD. I HAD A GOOD FRIEND WHILE I WAS IN HIGH SCHOOL NAMED MAX. HE ALSO WENT TO CANADA FREQUENTLY.... I WAS CURIOUS IF YOU WERE HIM. MAX GREEN? IF NOT , I WOULD LIKE TO CORRESPOND WITH YOU ANYWAY.... I HAVE A FEW QUESTIONS FOR YOU . MY EMAIL IS ....[email protected] SHOOT ME AN EMAIL..... THANKS, BOB

Hi, Does anyone know where I can get a map showing the names and locations of fishing resorts and lodges in the Souix Narrows/Kenora area? I have map that came with In-fisherman of the "Patrica" area with about 200 lodges and brief descriptions. I would like to look at the Kenora area before making a short list of choices for this summer's trip. Thanks, Nimstug
